      "position": 2,
      "properties": {
        "description": "<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Discuss:** *What are you most proud of about your project so far?*\n\n**Discussion Goal:** Students share what they are proud of about their project."
